OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FHaar in east soon becoming
OL,6,Fconfined to the immediate coast to
OL,7,Fleave a largely dry day with sunny
OL,8,Fspells, perhaps just the odd shower
OL,9,Fover the mountains. Very warm or hot
OL,10,Finland but much cooler on the east
OL,11,Fcoast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry, bright start this
OL,14,Fevening but outbreaks of heavy
OL,15,Fthundery rain, risk of torrential
OL,16,Fdownpours and hail, edging into Moray,
OL,17,Fand across the region overnight. Drier
OL,18,Flater in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
