OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA mostly dry start with some
OL,6,Fbrightness but outbreaks of heavy
OL,7,Fthundery rain near the east coast
OL,8,Fspread back northwest across the area
OL,9,Fthrough the day. Much cooler than
OL,10,Frecently.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FBright
OL,13,Fstart Saturday, some very warm
OL,14,Fsunshine for north coast, but cloud
OL,15,Fincreasing with showery rain later.
OL,16,FSunday and Monday see sunny spells and
OL,17,Fshowers, with a fresh southwesterly
OL,18,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
